highlights.text: Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Denmark. “DAISIES” is the highest at #1.
“Reposado” by Benny Jamz and Gilli has been on Top Songs Denmark the longest, at 386 days straight.

“What Did I Miss?” by Drake is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Denmark, up 54 spots at #63.
